HEADWORD: Speedwell
<hw>Speed"well</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the genus <gen>Veronica</gen>, mostly low herbs with
pale blue corollas, which quickly fall off.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Speedy</ent>⟦br⟧
